<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Diagnostic — La Traverse</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --night: #0d0f11;
    --night-card: #13161a;
    --night-light: #1a1d22;
    --night-hover: #1f2329;
    --copper: #c4622a;
    --copper-soft: rgba(196,98,42,0.15);
    --copper-glow: rgba(196,98,42,0.08);
    --gold: #d4a574;
    --text-bright: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    --text-mid: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    --text-dim: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    --ghost: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    --green: #3ecf8e;
    --blue: #6cb4ee;
    --amber: #f5a623;
    --rose: #e8788a;
    --violet: #a78bfa;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--night);
    color: var(--text-mid);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  ::selection { background: var(--copper); color: white; }

  /* ===== LAYOUT ===== */
  .page-wrapper {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 24px 100px;
  }

  /* ===== HEADER ===== */
  .diag-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ghost);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .diag-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--copper-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .diag-logo {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .diag-logo-sub {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--copper);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .diag-header h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    color: var(--text-bright);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .diag-header h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--copper); }

  .diag-header p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== PROGRESS BAR ===== */
  .progress-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding: 0 4px;
  }

  .progress-step {
    flex: 1;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: var(--ghost);
    transition: background 0.4s ease;
  }

  .progress-step.done { background: var(--copper); }
  .progress-step.active { background: var(--gold); }

  .progress-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ===== STEP CONTAINER ===== */
  .step {
    display: none;
    animation: stepIn 0.4s ease;
  }

  .step.active { display: block; }

  @keyframes stepIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .step-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .step-title em { color: var(--copper); font-style: italic; }

  .step-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* ===== FORM ELEMENTS ===== */
  .field-group {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .field-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .field-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .field-label .required { color: var(--copper); }

  .field-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  input[type="text"],
  input[type="email"],
  input[type="tel"],
  input[type="url"],
  textarea,
  select {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--night-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    outline: none;
  }

  input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus {
    border-color: var(--copper);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--copper-soft);
  }

  input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder { color: var(--text-dim); }

  textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 80px; }

  /* ===== PROFILE SELECTION ===== */
  .profile-select {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .profile-option {
    background: var(--night-card);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .profile-option:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .profile-option.selected {
    border-color: var(--copper);
    background: rgba(196,98,42,0.06);
  }

  .profile-option .p-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }

  .profile-option .p-name {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .profile-option .p-sub {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--copper);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .profile-option .p-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .profile-option input { display: none; }

  /* ===== SCENARIO SELECTION ===== */
  .scenario-select {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .scenario-option {
    background: var(--night-card);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .scenario-option:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
  .scenario-option.selected { border-color: var(--copper); background: rgba(196,98,42,0.06); }
  .scenario-option .s-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .scenario-option .s-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 500; }
  .scenario-option input { display: none; }

  /* ===== QUESTION BLOCK ===== */
  .question-block {
    background: var(--night-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .question-block:focus-within {
    border-color: rgba(196,98,42,0.3);
  }

  .question-block .q-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .question-block .q-label .q-num {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--copper);
    margin-top: 3px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .question-block .q-context {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-left: 28px;
  }

  .question-block textarea {
    background: var(--night-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    min-height: 60px;
  }

  /* ===== LAYER HEADER ===== */
  .layer-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ghost);
  }

  .layer-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .layer-icon.metier { background: rgba(62,207,142,0.12); color: var(--green); }
  .layer-icon.outils { background: rgba(108,180,238,0.12); color: var(--blue); }
  .layer-icon.tech { background: rgba(245,166,35,0.12); color: var(--amber); }
  .layer-icon.data { background: rgba(232,120,138,0.12); color: var(--rose); }
  .layer-icon.ia { background: rgba(167,139,250,0.12); color: var(--violet); }
  .layer-icon.friction { background: rgba(196,98,42,0.12); color: var(--copper); }

  .layer-name {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-bright);
  }

  .layer-badge {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--ghost);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  /* ===== CHECKLIST ===== */
  .checklist-category {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .checklist-cat-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .checklist-cat-header h4 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-bright);
  }

  .checklist-badge {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .checklist-badge.all { background: rgba(62,207,142,0.12); color: var(--green); }
  .checklist-badge.tech { background: rgba(245,166,35,0.12); color: var(--amber); }
  .checklist-badge.ia { background: rgba(167,139,250,0.12); color: var(--violet); }
  .checklist-badge.ecom { background: rgba(232,120,138,0.12); color: var(--rose); }

  .checklist-items {
    background: var(--night-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .checklist-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ghost);
    transition: background 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .checklist-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .checklist-item:hover { background: var(--night-hover); }

  .checklist-item input[type="checkbox"] {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    accent-color: var(--copper);
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .checklist-item label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    cursor: pointer;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .checklist-item .upload-slot {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--copper);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--copper-soft);
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .checklist-item .upload-slot:hover {
    background: var(--copper-soft);
  }

  /* ===== ACCESS FIELDS ===== */
  .access-section {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .access-section h4 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .access-section .access-scope {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .access-field {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ghost);
  }

  .access-field:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .access-field .access-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--copper);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .access-field .access-name {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .access-field input {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--night-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.25s;
  }

  .access-field input:focus { border-color: var(--copper); }
  .access-field input::placeholder { color: var(--text-dim); }

  /* ===== HUMAN AUDIT ===== */
  .human-block {
    background: var(--night-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .human-block h4 {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .human-block .human-context {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== BUTTONS ===== */
  .nav-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ghost);
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    border: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .btn-prev {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-mid);
  }

  .btn-prev:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: var(--text-bright); }

  .btn-next {
    background: var(--copper);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-next:hover { background: #d4722e; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .btn-next:disabled {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    transform: none;
  }

  .btn-submit {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #0d0f11;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .btn-submit:hover { background: #4dd89a; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* ===== CONFIRMATION ===== */
  .confirmation {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 20px;
  }

  .confirmation .conf-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(62,207,142,0.12);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 36px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
  }

  .confirmation h2 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .confirmation p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .confirmation .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 32px;
    color: var(--copper);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .confirmation .back-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ===== CONDITIONAL ===== */
  .tech-only { display: none; }
  body.profile-equipe .tech-only,
  body.profile-migrant .tech-only { display: block; }

  /* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .field-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .profile-select { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .scenario-select { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .access-field { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 6px; }
    .access-field .access-name { min-width: auto; }
    .access-field input { width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-wrapper">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="diag-header">
    <div class="diag-logo">La Traverse</div>
    <div class="diag-logo-sub">Diagnostic Client</div>
    <h1>Aidez-nous a vous <em>comprendre</em></h1>
    <p>Ce formulaire nous permet de cartographier votre activite, vos outils et vos besoins pour vous proposer la meilleure route possible.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- PROGRESS -->
  <div class="progress-label" id="progressLabel">Etape 1 sur 7</div>
  <div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar">
    <div class="progress-step active"></div>
    <div class="progress-step"></div>
    <div class="progress-step"></div>
    <div class="progress-step"></div>
    <div class="progress-step"></div>
    <div class="progress-step"></div>
    <div class="progress-step"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ========== STEP 1 : COORDONNEES ========== -->
  <div class="step active" data-step="1">
    <h2 class="step-title">Vos <em>coordonnees</em></h2>
    <p class="step-desc">Pour qu'on puisse vous recontacter et preparer votre diagnostic.</p>

    <div class="field-row">
      <div class="field-group">
        <label class="field-label">Votre nom <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="client_name" placeholder="Jean Dupont" required>
      </div>
      <div class="field-group">
        <label class="field-label">Nom de l'entreprise</label>
        <input type="text" id="client_company" placeholder="Mon Entreprise SARL">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="field-row">
      <div class="field-group">
        <label class="field-label">Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="email" id="client_email" placeholder="jean@monentreprise.fr" required>
      </div>
      <div class="field-group">
        <label class="field-label">Telephone</label>
        <input type="tel" id="client_phone" placeholder="06 12 34 56 78">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="field-group">
      <label class="field-label">Site web actuel</label>
      <input type="url" id="client_website" placeholder="https://monentreprise.fr">
      <div class="field-hint">Laissez vide si vous n'en avez pas encore</div>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-buttons">
      <div></div>
      <button class="btn btn-next" onclick="goToStep(2)">Continuer</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ========== STEP 2 : PROFIL & SCENARIO ========== -->
  <div class="step" data-step="2">
    <h2 class="step-title">Votre <em>situation</em></h2>
    <p class="step-desc">Choisissez le profil qui vous ressemble le plus, et le type de projet envisage.</p>

    <label class="field-label" style="margin-bottom:14px">Quel profil vous correspond ? <span class="required">*</span></label>
    <div class="profile-select">
      <div class="profile-option" onclick="selectProfile(this, 'vierge')">
        <input type="radio" name="profile" value="vierge">
        <div class="p-icon">🌱</div>
        <div class="p-sub">Profil A</div>
        <div class="p-name">Le Vierge</div>
        <div class="p-desc">Pas de tech, ou juste un site basique et des tableurs. Tout est a creer.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="profile-option" onclick="selectProfile(this, 'equipe')">
        <input type="radio" name="profile" value="equipe">
        <div class="p-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="p-sub">Profil B</div>
        <div class="p-name">L'Equipe</div>
        <div class="p-desc">Deja un SaaS, CRM, ou e-commerce. Vous voulez greffer quelque chose dessus.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="profile-option" onclick="selectProfile(this, 'migrant')">
        <input type="radio" name="profile" value="migrant">
        <div class="p-icon">🔄</div>
        <div class="p-sub">Profil C</div>
        <div class="p-name">Le Migrant</div>
        <div class="p-desc">Un outil qui marche mais devenu un frein. Trop lent, trop cher, plus maintenu.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <label class="field-label" style="margin-bottom:14px">Quel type de projet ? <span class="required">*</span></label>
    <div class="scenario-select">
      <div class="scenario-option" onclick="selectScenario(this, 'saas')">
        <input type="radio" name="scenario" value="saas">
        <div class="s-icon">🧩</div>
        <div class="s-label">SaaS existant</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scenario-option" onclick="selectScenario(this, 'scratch')">
        <input type="radio" name="scenario" value="scratch">
        <div class="s-icon">🌱</div>
        <div class="s-label">From scratch</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scenario-option" onclick="selectScenario(this, 'migration')">
        <input type="radio" name="scenario" value="migration">
        <div class="s-icon">🔄</div>
        <div class="s-label">Migration</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scenario-option" onclick="selectScenario(this, 'ecommerce')">
        <input type="radio" name="scenario" value="ecommerce">
        <div class="s-icon">🛒</div>
        <div class="s-label">E-commerce</div>
      </div>
      <div class="scenario-option" onclick="selectScenario(this, 'ia')">
